A yet to be identified Nigerian man has reportedly taken his life after his girlfriend of 7 years dumped him. It was gathered that the man took his life at his apartment by hanging himself with a rope. A new video that was shared online shows the moment people were trying to remove the rope from his neck at the victim’s apartment. Someone could be heard in the video saying: “Hey, nobody dey here? You just killed yourself for nothing, because of woman!” It was not stated which particular state the sad incident took place. Click the link below to watch video: https://www.instagram.com/p/ByYN5FLj4Mw/?igshid=1g63kp57eumgg Source